Who needs a 🧡 FROZEN FRAPPE 🧡  to cool off this summer? ⁠
⁠
3 oz. Blue Chair Bay® Mango Rum Cream⁠
1.5 oz. black tea⁠
1 oz. pineapple juice⁠
.5 oz. simple syrup⁠
1.5 cups ice⁠
⁠
Put all ingredients into a blender. Blend. Pour into a glass and garnish with fat free whipped cream and a cherry.
